    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Breast ornaments worn by Jewish high priests. Traditionally comprising a folded piece of embroidered linen worn on the breast, and adorned with twelve precious stones, representing the twelve tribes.</Note_Text>
